.SH NAME
imperial2metric \- Convert imperial/customary units to metric system
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B imperial2metric
.I COMMAND VALUE
[\fI\,OPTIONS\fR]
.PP
.B imperial2metric
.BR \-\-update
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B imperial2metric
is a unit conversion utility that converts imperial and US customary measurements to metric system equivalents using bc (basic calculator) for precise arithmetic. It supports temperature, length, weight, and currency conversions with configurable decimal precision and optional desktop notifications for results.
.PP
The script simplifies unit conversion by providing command-line temperature conversion (Fahrenheit to Celsius), length conversion (inches, feet, yards, miles to metric), weight conversion (pounds to kilograms), currency conversion (USD to EUR) with live exchange rates, bc-based arithmetic for precision (2 decimal places), desktop notification integration for results, and automatic exchange rate updates via forex API.
.PP
imperial2metric is particularly useful for quick CLI unit conversions, international measurement system translation, scientific and engineering calculations, shell script integration for conversions, and automated unit conversion in workflows.
