How imperial2metric converts temperature:
.SS Fahrenheit to Celsius
.RS
.EX
Formula: (°F - 32) × 5/9 = °C

imperial2metric f 32
# Output: 32 Fahrenheit is 0.00 celcius

imperial2metric f 212
# Output: 212 Fahrenheit is 100.00 celcius
